# Test Cases

| TC ID | Title | Preconditions | Steps | Expected Result | Priority |
|-------|-------|--------------|-------|----------------|----------|
| TC-01 | User Registration with valid data | User not logged in | 1. Open registration page 2. Enter valid data 3. Submit | User account created successfully | High |
| TC-02 | Registration with invalid email | Registration page open | 1. Enter invalid email format 2. Submit | Error message displayed | High |
| TC-03 | Login with valid credentials | User registered | 1. Enter valid credentials 2. Login | User redirected to account page | High |
| TC-04 | Login with invalid password | User registered | 1. Enter wrong password 2. Login | Error message displayed | High |
| TC-05 | Add product to cart | Product page open | 1. Click Add to Cart | Product added to cart | High |
| TC-06 | Update product quantity | Product in cart | 1. Change quantity 2. Update cart | Quantity updated correctly | Medium |
| TC-07 | Remove product from cart | Product in cart | 1. Click Remove | Product removed | Medium |
| TC-08 | Checkout with valid data | Product in cart | 1. Proceed to checkout 2. Fill valid details 3. Confirm | Order successfully placed | High |
| TC-09 | Checkout with empty required fields | On checkout page | 1. Leave required fields empty 2. Submit | Validation errors displayed | High |
| TC-10 | Search product by name | Home page open | 1. Enter product name 2. Search | Relevant results displayed | Medium |
